    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = ((0.18 + (tmp + 0.88 + v2 + 0.93)) / v0)
    v1 = ((v2 * wp.cos(v0 + 0.80)) + tmp)
    v0 = 0.88
    v2 = wp.cos(wp.exp((v0 + 0.82 + v1 + 0.76)))
    v1 = wp.exp((wp.cos(v2 + 0.89) - (v1 + 0.28 * v0 + 0.47)))
    tmp = (0.29 * (wp.abs(v2 + 0.24) + 0.79))
    v0 = (v2 + 0.96)
    data[tid] = v0
